These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, hot-chocolate, mirinda, tea
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: balloon-flower, daffodil, begonia, lily
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person drinking cola and the person who growsdaffodil##2
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person who growsballoon-flower##3
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the person drinking cola##7
4. the person who growsdaffodil is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
6. the person who growsdaffodil is somewhere to the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | mirinda | tea       | hot-chocolate | cola        |
| Flower      | begonia  | daffodil | lily        | balloon-flower |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
House: futuristic, modern, victorian, colonial
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cycling, rowing, skateboarding, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is volleyball is somewhere between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the victorian house##7
2. the colonial house is somewhere to the left of the futuristic house##5
3. the colonial house is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##5
4. the modern house is on the left of the colonial house##1
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the person who's sport is rowing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| House     | victorian | modern       | colonial         | futuristic     |
| Sport   | rowing   | volleyball | skateboarding | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, crime, mystery, scientific
City: berlin, new-york, san-francisco, edinburgh
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is somewhere between the person traveling to new-york and the person traveling to berlin##7
3. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
4. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere between the person traveling to edinburgh and the person watching crime movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | scientific | mystery | comedy  |
| City   | san-francisco | berlin  | edinburgh   | new-york |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, traveling, woodworking, writing
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, november, december, april
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is collecting is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in november and the person who's hobby is writing##7
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person who's birthday is in april##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Hobby   | traveling | collecting | writing       | woodworking |
| Birthday   | november      | september   | december | april  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, reading, rock-climbing, video-games
4 different pets are kept: goat, dog, snake, pony
1. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
2. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the dog##5
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
4. the owner of the pony is somewhere between the person who's hobby is reading and the person who's hobby is drawing##7
5. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
6. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the left of the owner of the pony##5
7. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | drawing   | video-games | reading |
| Pet   | goat      | dog | pony      | snake |

