.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, time-travel, romance, superhero
There are 4 different nationalities: american, dutch, indonesian, nigerian
1. the person watching romance movies is on the left of the indonesian##1
2. the indonesian is the person watching superhero movies##1
3. the dutch is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
4. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching romance movies##1
5. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left or right of the nigerian##3
6. the nigerian is somewhere between the american and the dutch##7
7. the indonesian is somewhere to the right of the person watching romance movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre      | time-travel | zombie      | romance | superhero     |
| Nationality   | american    | nigerian | dutch   | indonesian |

