2. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the chinese##1
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the far left or far right##3
4. the spanish is somewhere between the person watching spy movies and the person watching romance movies##7
5. the nigerian is somewhere to the left of the person watching romance movies##5
6. the spanish is on the left or right of the nigerian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre          | fantasy    | spy   | documentary | romance  |
| Nationality   | argentine | nigerian | spanish    | chinese |

