.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, argentine, colombian, spanish
4 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble, go, canasta
1. the argentine is not the person playing canasta##6
2. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3
3. the spanish is the person playing go##1
4. the colombian is somewhere between the spanish and the american##7
5. the argentine is on the left of the american##1
6. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person playing go##1
7. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | spanish | colombian | argentine | american |
| Game           | go   | canasta    | backgammon       | scrabble  |

