.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  engineer, police-officer, scientist, security-guard
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, juice, almond-milk, milk
1. the engineer is not the person drinking 7up##6
2. the scientist is on the right of the engineer##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the engineer##3
4. the engineer is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
5. the scientist is somewhere between the person drinking milk and the police-officer##7
6. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the right of the person drinking almond-milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |       4        |
| Job           | security-guard | engineer | scientist | police-officer |
| Beverage   | milk         | almond-milk      | 7up | juice            |

