2. the person watching satire movies is not the videographer##6
3. the designer is not the person watching thriller movies##6
4. the person watching thriller movies is somewhere to the right of the police-officer##5
5. the person watching family movies is the musician##1
6. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the right of the musician##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
