The people prefer 4 different music-genres: gospel, hip-hop, house, indie
1. the fan of hip-hop is in an even position##4
2. the fan of indie is somewhere between the person who's sport is rugby and the fan of house##7
3. the fan of indie is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
4. the fan of house is in an even position##4
5. the person who's sport is weightlifting is somewhere to the left of the fan of hip-hop##5
6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the fan of house##1
7. the person who's sport is biathlon is the fan of indie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
| Sport      | weightlifting   | tennis | biathlon | rugby   |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | house   | indie | hip-hop |

