The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, firefighter, freelancer, paramedic
1. the dunhill-smoker is somewhere between the ritmeester-smoker and the paramedic##7
2. the architect is somewhere to the right of the firefighter##5
3. the paramedic is on the far left##1
4. the ritmeester-smoker is not the paramedic##6
5. the old-henry-smoker is somewhere between the architect and the freelancer##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Cigar   | pall-mall | dunhill     | old-henry     | ritmeester |
| Job     | paramedic | freelancer | firefighter | architect     |

