2. the nurse is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bike##5
3. the manager is not the person driving the taxi##6
4. the nurse is somewhere to the left of the person driving the taxi##5
5. the person driving the train is somewhere between the person driving the ship and the manager##7
6. the person driving the train is on the left of the freelancer##1
7. the teacher is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Job           | manager | nurse  | freelancer  | teacher |
| Transport   | bike  | train | taxi | ship   |

