.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, rowing, swimming, baseball
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, motorbike, quad-bike, scooter
1. the person who's sport is swimming is somewhere between the person driving the bus and the person who's sport is rowing##7
2. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is swimming##5
5. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Sport         | rowing    | swimming | baseball     | basketball |
| Transport   | quad-bike | scooter  | motorbike | bus |

 